C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729938181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671a9cea01ea6d83dee3e2ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felection-day-jitters-mean-some-shoppers-may-may-fewer-purchases-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Companies%20from%20United%20Airlines%20to%20Nestl%C3%A9%20have%20pointed%20to%20election%20day%20as%20a%20slow%20time%20for%20sales.%20Some%20customers%20do%20appear%20to%20be%20holding%20back.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abitter%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felection-day-jitters-mean-some-shoppers-may-may-fewer-purchases-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFeeling%20Betrayed%26quot%3B%3A%20Indian%20PhD%20Student%20Moved%20To%20Master's%20Course%20At%20Oxford%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAn%20Indian%20PhD%20student%20has%20accused%20the%20University%20of%20Oxford%20of%20transferring%20her%20to%20a%20master's%20course%20against%20her%20will%2C%20describing%20the%20experience%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbetrayal.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ELakshmi%20Balakrishnan%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20invested%20nearly%20%C2%A3100%2C000%20(around%20Rs%201.09%20crore)%20in%20her%20education%20and%20living%20expenses%20at%20the%20institution%2C%20where%20she%20aimed%20to%20pursue%20her%20doctoral%20studies%20in%20English%20literature%2C%20reported%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcy898dzknzgo%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMs%20Balakrishnan%20said%20that%20the%20English%20faculty%20has%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20acted%20in%20good%20faith%E2%80%9D%20after%20initially%20accepting%20her%20thesis%20proposal%20at%20both%20the%20application%20stage%20and%20during%20her%20first%20year.%20Later%2C%20the%20faculty%20rejected%20her%20research%20idea%20in%20her%20fourth%20year%2C%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20forcibly%20removed%20me%20from%20the%20PhD%20program%20and%20moved%20me%20to%20a%20masters%20level%20course%20without%20my%20consent.%20I%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20betrayal%20and%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20have%20been%20let%20down%20by%20an%20institution%20that%20I%20held%20in%20high%20regard.%20I%20already%20have%20two%20masters%20degrees%20from%20India%20and%20I%20paid%20%C2%A3100%2C000%20at%20Oxford%20to%20get%20my%20PhD%2C%20not%20another%20masters%20course%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20BBC%20quoted%20Balakrishnan%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERaised%20in%20south%20India%20by%20her%20father%20after%20losing%20her%20mother%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20Lakshmi%20Balakrishnan%20said%20she%20was%20the%20first%20member%20of%20her%20family%20to%20study%20abroad%2C%20overcoming%20significant%20challenges%20to%20enrol%20at%20Oxford.%20%E2%80%9CI%20hail%20from%20an%20underprivileged%20background%2C%20I%20made%20immense%20sacrifices%20to%20come%20and%20study%20at%20Oxford%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDuring%20her%20fourth%20year%2C%20Ms%20Balakrishnan%20underwent%20an%20assessment%20where%20two%20different%20assessors%20deemed%20her%20Shakespeare%20research%20insufficient%20for%20PhD-level%20study.%20She%20contested%20the%20faculty's%20decision%20and%20entered%20an%20appeals%20process%20but%20reported%20that%20her%20efforts%20were%20unsuccessful.%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20that%20the%20university's%20strategy%20is%20to%20force%20me%20to%20wade%20through%20endless%20appeals%20and%20complaints%20procedures%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20I%20will%20eventually%20give%20up%20and%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20appeals%20process%20has%20now%20concluded%2C%20with%20Oxford%20University%20stating%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20achieve%20Confirmation%20of%20Status%2C%20progress%20must%20sufficiently%20demonstrate%20a%20strong%20likelihood%20of%20successful%20completion%20of%20a%20doctoral%20thesis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Queen's%20College%2C%20where%20Ms%20Balakrishnan%20was%20enrolled%2C%20has%20expressed%20concern%20regarding%20her%20treatment.%20The%20college%20noted%20that%20while%20she%20failed%20two%20assessments%2C%20there%20were%20no%20serious%20concerns%20highlighted%20in%20her%20term%20reports.%20In%20addition%2C%20two%20Shakespeare%20scholars%20have%20endorsed%20her%20research%2C%20stating%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20for%20a%20PhD%2C%20stated%20the%20BBC%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDespite%20these%20endorsements%2C%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Independent%20Adjudicator%20(OIA)%20supported%20the%20university's%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729938000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Feggu3rps_university-of-oxford_625x300_26_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findian-phd-student-alleges-forcible-transfer-to-master-s-course-at-oxford-university-6876916%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20student%20accused%20the%20English%20faculty%20of%20having%20%26quot%3Bnot%20acted%20in%20good%20faith%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bobby%20Deol%3A%20I%20can't%20speak%20Tamil%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729937716000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114620116%2Cimgsize-88270.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbobby-deol-i-cant-speak-tamil-siva-has-found-the-perfect-voice-to-bring-udhiran-to-life-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F114620119.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bobby%20Deol