ur%20monthly%20payment%20by%20%24200%2C%20it%20would%20take%20you%2015%20months%20to%20break%20even%20on%20your%20refinance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Rate%20Trends%5C%22%3E5-Year%20Mortgage%20Rate%20Trends%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%2030-year%20and%2015-year%20mortgage%20rates%20have%20trended%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20according%20to%20Freddie%20Mac%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FdBxcL%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Weekly%20mortgage%20rates%20over%20the%20last%205%20years%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22503%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20Factors%20Influence%20Mortgage%20Rates%3F%5C%22%3EWhat%20Factors%20Influence%20Mortgage%20Rates%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fhow-are-mortgage-rates-determined%5C%22%3EMortgage%20rates%20are%20determined%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20a%20variety%20of%20different%20factors%2C%20including%20larger%20economic%20trends%2C%20Federal%20Reserve%20policy%2C%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fstate-mortgage-rates%5C%22%3Estate's%20current%20mortgage%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20type%20of%20loan%20you're%20getting%2C%20and%20your%20personal%20financial%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20of%20these%20factors%20are%20out%20of%20your%20control%2C%20you%20can%20work%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fhow-to-improve-credit-score%5C%22%3Eimproving%20your%20credit%20score%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20paying%20off%20debt%2C%20and%20saving%20for%20a%20larger%20down%20payment%20to%20ensure%20you%20get%20the%20best%20rate%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20Does%20the%20Fed%20Rate%20Affect%20Mortgage%20Rates%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed%20increased%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-the-federal-funds-rate%5C%22%3Efederal%20funds%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20dramatically%20in%202022%20and%202023%20to%20try%20to%20slow%20economic%20growth%20and%20get%20inflation%20under%20control.%20Inflation%20has%20since%20slowed%20significantly%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20a%20bit%20above%20the%20Fed's%202%25%20target%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20aren't%20directly%20impacted%20by%20changes%20to%20the%20federal%20funds%20rate%2C%20but%20they%20often%20trend%20up%20or%20down%20ahead%20of%20Fed%20policy%20moves.%20This%20is%20because%20mortgage%20rates%20change%20based%20on%20investor%20demand%20for%20mortgage-backed%20securities%2C%20and%20this%20demand%20is%20often%20impacted%20by%20how%20investors%20expect%20Fed%20policy%20to%20affect%20the%20broader%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed%20recently%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-cuts-interest-rates-how-much-september-fomc-powell-inflation-2024-9%5C%22%3Elower%20rates%20by%2050%20basis%20points%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Mortgage%20rates%20trended%20down%20ahead%20of%20this%20decision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Mortgage%20Rate%20Projection%20for%202024%5C%22%3EMortgage%20Rate%20Projection%20for%202024%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fwill-mortgage-rates-go-down-this-year%5C%22%3EMortgage%20rates%20are%20expected%20to%20go%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202025%2C%20but%20they%20may%20not%20drop%20much%20further%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20started%20ticking%20up%20from%20historic%20lows%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%202021%20and%20increased%20dramatically%20in%202022%20and%20throughout%20most%20of%202023.%20But%20now%20that%20inflation%20has%20decelerated%20and%20the%20Fed%20is%20expected%20to%20cut%20rates%20soon%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20have%20trended%20down.%20In%20the%20last