ly%20say%20men%20in%20their%2020s%20have%20around%20400%20to%20600.%20For%20Kade%2C%20this%20was%20a%20glimmer%20of%20hope%3A%20finally%2C%20something%20he%20could%20try%20to%20fix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20later%2C%20you%20can%20find%20Kade%20on%20TikTok%2C%20telling%2074%2C000%20followers%20he%20transformed%20his%20well-being%20%E2%80%94%20and%20body%20composition%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20regimen%20of%20twice%20weekly%20testosterone%20injections.%20At%2025%2C%20he%20feels%20like%20a%20new%20man%2C%20he%20said.%20He's%20healthy%2C%20muscular%2C%20lean%2C%20full-bearded%2C%20and%20horny.%20He%20said%20his%20sex%20drive%20is%20%26quot%3Buncaged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20your%20soldier%20is%20not%20standing%20at%20full%20salute%20or%20your%20tent%20is%20not%20fully%20pitched%2C%20you%20have%20low%20testosterone%2C%26quot%3B%20Kade%2C%20who%20doesn't%20use%20his%20last%20name%20publicly%2C%20said%20in%20one%20video%2C%20punctuating%20his%20sentences%20with%20the%20occasional%20swing%20of%20a%20syringe.%20People%20comment%20on%20his%20page%20asking%20for%20more%20information%20about%20his%20doses.%20He%20tells%20them%20to%20check%20out%20LaSara%20Medical%20Group%2C%20a%20virtual%20clinic%20for%20men's%20sexual%20health.%20(LaSara%20confirmed%20Kade%20gets%20free%20treatments%20in%20exchange%20for%20referrals.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKade's%20story%20is%20not%20unique.%20He%20represents%20a%20growing%20swath%20of%20young%20men%20turning%20to%20testosterone-replacement%20therapy%20(also%20known%20as%20TRT%20or%20simply%20T)%20to%2C%20in%20their%20view%2C%20optimize%20their%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221634%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alexis%20Ohanian%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67191d469b3250dbbce979ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222451%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlexis%20Ohanian%2C%2041%2C%20recently%20posted%20his%20T%20levels%20on%20X.%3Cp%3EBryan%20Bedder%2FAthlos%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Athlos%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20taboo%20%E2%80%94%20a%20private%20matter%20for%20an%20older%20guy%20with%20erectile%20dysfunction%20or%20a%20hormonal%20deficiency%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20now%20become%20a%20point%20of%20pride%20for%20men%20to%20proactively%20track%20their%20testosterone%20levels%20and%20confront%20dips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20Alexis%20Ohanian%2C%20the%2041-year-old%20Reddit%20cofounder%20and%20Serena%20Williams'%20husband%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Falexisohanian%2Fstatus%2F1813220215263490418%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%20posted%20on%20X%20about%20his%20(relatively%20high)%20testosterone%20levels%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20credited%20weightlifting%2C%20cutting%20down%20on%20meat%20and%20alcohol%2C%20and%20taking%20testosterone-support%20supplements%20from%20the%20healthcare%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexis-ohanian-on-investing-in-healthcare-startup-ro-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20he%20is%20an%20investor.%20In%202018%2C%20Joe%20Rogan%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEEce1DRsRwQ%26ab_channel%3DJREClips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epodcast%20listeners%20he%20started%20TRT%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he%20turned%2040%20to%20make%20his%20body%20%26quot%3Bwork%20way%20better.%26quot%3B%20In%202021%2C%20the%20actor%20Dax%20Shepard%2C%20then%2046%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farmchairexpertpod.com%2Fpods%2Fmila-kunis-ashton-kutcher%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20podcast%20that%20he%20had%20gained%2024%20pounds%20of%20muscle%20thanks%2C%20in%20part%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Bheavy%20testosterone%20injections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20primary-care%20doctors%20may%20recommend%20diet%20tweaks%20and%20better%20sleep%20to%20naturally%20boost%20testosterone%20levels%2C%20a%20booming%20industry%20of%20men's%20clinics%20offers%20more%20potent%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrescriptions%20for%20testosterone-replacement%20therapy%20have%20dramatically%20increased%20across%20the%20US%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20rising%2020%25%20from%202016%20to%202019.%20More%20recent%20data%2C%20while%20limited%20due%20to%20inconsistent%20monitoring%2C%20suggests%20the%20rate%20is%20steadily%20climbing.%20Only%20a%20tiny%20fraction%20of%20that%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20trans%20healthcare%3B%200.3%25%20of%20the%20US%20population%20is%20trans%2C%20according%20to%20the%20CDC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20trend%20tells%20a%20story%20of%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20gender-affirming%20care%2C%20but%20for%20cisgender%20men.%20Testosterone%20is%20prescribed%20to%20treat%20a%20set%20of%20vague%20symptoms%20for%20men%20hoping%20to%20feel%20%26quot%3Bbetter%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20it's%20not%20exactly%20clear%20what%20it%20does%20or%20who%20needs%20it.%20In%20his%202007%20analysis%20of%20the%20testosterone%20market%2C%20the%20legendary%20medical%20sociologist%20Peter%20Conrad%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BTestosterone%20became%20a%20drug%20in%20search%20of%20a%20disease%20to%20treat.%26quot%3B%20Nearly%20two%20decades%20later%2C%20the%20search%20continues%2C%20with%20male%20insecurity%20as%20a%20stand-in%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2281b47440-5d40-4eab-8b35-778b613a6cde%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20house%20that%20Viagra%20built%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20fascination%20with%20testosterone%20dates%20back%20to%20over%20a%20century%20ago%2C%20when%20endocrinologists%20found%20that%20testosterone%20is%20associated%20with%20male%20aging.%20In%201889%2C%20Charles-%C3%89douard%20Brown-S%C3%A9quard%2C%20an%20eccentric%20French%20physiologist%2C%20injected%20himself%20with%20testicular%20blood%20and%20seminal%20fluids%20from%20dogs%20and%20guinea%20pigs%2C%20saying%20the%20experiment%20rejuvenated%20his%20energy%20and%20libido%20at%2072.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20now%20know%20that%20is%20impossible%20based%20on%20how%20testicles%20store%20hormones%20%E2%80%94%20at%20best%2C%20it%20was%20a%20placebo%20effect%20%E2%80%94%20the%20concept%20kick-started%20a%20new%20era%20of%20hormone%20research.%20What%20followed%20was%20a%20century%20of%20patchy%20research%2C%20with%20some%20groundbreaking%20discoveries%20that%20shaped%20the%20modern%20era%20of%20trans%20care%20but%20not%20enough%20clarity%20to%20warrant%20widespread%20testosterone%20prescriptions%20for%20cisgender%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Charles-%C3%89douard%20Brown-S%C3%A9quard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671ab9e201ea6d83dee3f6c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22653%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharles-%C3%89douard%20Brown-S%C3%A9quard's%20experiments%20%E2%80%94%20using%20animals'%20testicles%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20rejuvenate%20old%20men%20%E2%80%94%20made%20such%20a%20splash%20they%20were%20satirized.%20This%20cartoon%20was%20published%20in%201896%20in%20the%20weekly%20magazine%2C%20Judge.%3Cp%3EArchival%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20story%20of%20today's%20testosterone%20clinics%20begins%20in%202017%2C%20with%20Viagra%20coming%20off%20patent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViagra%2C%20a%20vasodilator%20that%20can%20help%20men%20achieve%20an%20erection%2C%20created%20an%20industry%20to%20medically%20treat%20masculinity%20in%20a%20way%20never%20seen%20before.%20When%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20generic%20form%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fbrucelee%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2Fviagra-get-ready-for-it-to-becomes-generic-cheaper-and-more-available%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentered%20the%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20little%20blue%20pill%20dropped%20in%20cost%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC8272595%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOver%2520the%2520last%2520decade%252C%2520sildenafil%2Cpill%2520for%2520a%2520generic%2520version.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2488.45%20a%20pill%20to%20%241%20to%20%244%3C%2Fa%3E%20apiece.%20Direct-to-consumer%20telehealth%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20startups%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vice.com%2Fen%2Farticle%2Ferectile-dysfunction-hims-roman-thinx-subway-ads%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHims%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Ro%20%E2%80%94%20popped%20up%2C%20offering%20consultations%20and%20treatments%20for%20conditions%20that%20were%20historically%20taboo%20to%20talk%20about%2C%20such%20as%20erectile%20dysfunction%20and%20hair%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPopularly%20known%20as%20the%20hormone%20responsible%20for%20making%20a%20man%20%26quot%3Bmanly%2C%26quot%3B%20testosterone%20was%20the%20natural%20next%20step%20in%20this%20growing%20healthcare%20market.%20Now%2C%20you%20can%20go%20to%20a%20clinic%20to%20fix%20more%20than%20just%20the%20strength%20of%20your%20erections%20and%20the%20hair%20on%20your%20head.%20Testosterone%20therapy%20promises%20to%20make%20you%20more%20muscular%2C%20hornier%2C%20and%20more%20driven.%20By%20conventional%20definitions%2C%20it%20promises%20to%20make%20you%20more%20of%20a%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%202017%20and%202019%2C%20some%20of%20the%20leading%20DTC%20men's%20websites%20saw%20a%201688%25%20increase%20in%20unique%20visits%2C%20averaging%205%20million%20visits%20a%20month%2C%20a%20study%20published%20in%20Sexual%20Medicine%20found.%20DTC%20health%20companies%20and%20telehealth%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1007%2Fs11930-022-00332-z%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtinued%20to%20expand%20since%20their%20explosion%20during%20the%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20these%20figures%20are%20even%20larger%20today.%20%26quot%3BThis%20business%20model%20practically%20built%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Justin%20Houman%2C%20a%20urologist%20and%20assistant%20professor%20at%20Cedars-Sinai%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnam02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252F10.0.82.45%252Ftau.2019.08.33%26data%3D05%257C02%257CAndrea.Becker%2540Hunter.cuny.edu%257C14c079dd6d3f43cd6e0c08dced2669a0%257C6f60f0b35f064e099715989dba8cc7d8%257C0%257C0%257C638645996446620828%257CUnknown%257CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%253D%257C0%257C%257C%257C%26sdata%3DcXW556nmD5VyU5BES5E6R9m2HSW2X6VrtGo6mH4bsiQ%253D%26reserved%3D0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanalysis%20of%20the%20men's%20health%20clinic%3C%2Fa%3E%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225831%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22New%20York%20City%20subway%20ads%20for%20Ro's%20generic%20version%20of%20Viagra%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671bf70101ea6d83dee451be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223887%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20Viagra%20came%20off%20patent%2C%20direct-to-consumer%20telehealth%20companies%20started%20popping%20up%2C%20offering%20more%20accessible%20treatments%20for%20erectile%20dysfunction%20and%20hair%20loss.%20One%20startup%2C%20Ro%2C%20advertised%20its%20generic%20ED%20treatment%20on%20New%20York%20City%20subways.%3Cp%3ERo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20LaSara's%20cofounder%20John%20Snedegar%20opened%20up%20his%20brick-and-mortar%20men's%20health%20clinic%20in%202017%2C%20%26quot%3Bnobody%26quot%3B%20was%20specializing%20in%20men's%20sexual%20health%2C%20he%20said.%20A%20urologist%20might%20check%20your%20testosterone%20levels%20if%20you%20were%20over%20the%20age%20of%2040%20and%20struggling%20with%20sex%20or%20fertility.%20Seven%20years%20later%2C%20his%20clinic%20is%20a%20tiny%20fish%20in%20an%20ocean%20of%20thousands%20of%20competitors%20offering%20specialized%20testosterone%20therapies%20to%20healthy%20men%20of%20all%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20used%20to%20be%20considered%20an%20old%20men's%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20Snedegar%2C%20an%20entrepreneur%20and%20former%20yoga%20instructor%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20we%20have%20patients%20in%20their%2020s%20and%20their%2030s%20and%20their%2040s%20with%20low%20testosterone%20seeking%20treatment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20it%20typically%20works%3A%20You%20sign%20up%20on%20a%20clinic's%20website%2C%20answer%20questions%20about%20your%20energy%2C%20happiness%2C%20erections%2C%20and%20sex%20drive%2C%20and%20maybe%20do%20a%20phone%20consultation.%20Some%20clinics%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.maximustribe.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaximus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20telehealth%20company%2C%20ship%20an%20at-home%20testing%20kit%20to%20you%20to%20assess%20your%20testosterone%20levels.%20In-house%20doctors%20review%20and%20approve%20your%20test%20results%3B%20the%20website%20assures%20prospective%20customers%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%20need%20to%20sweat%20it.%20Most%20men%20are%20approved%20for%20treatment.%26quot%3B%20Other%20clinics%2C%20such%20as%20LaSara%2C%20require%20blood%20work%20to%20be%20done%20in%20an%20affiliated%20lab%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20testosterone%20treatment%20is%20typically%20presented%20to%20patients%20as%20a%20lifelong%20endeavor%20(it%20can%20affect%20your%20natural%20production%20of%20testosterone%2C%20and%20attempting%20to%20stop%20TRT%20can%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F26742589%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bwithdrawal%26quot%3B%20effects%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20weight%20gain)%2C%20men's%20health%20clinics%20typically%20offer%20all-inclusive%20membership%20models.%20You%20pay%20a%20couple%20of%20hundred%20dollars%20a%20month%2C%20and%20that%20covers%20your%20lab%20work%20and%20injection%20therapy.%20At%20LaSara%2C%20patients%20pay%20%24170%20a%20month%20for%20shots%2C%20consultations%2C%20and%20lab%20work.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flowtcenter.com%2Fself-testosterone-injections%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELow%20T%20Center%2C%20headquartered%20in%20Texas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20offers%20prescriptions%20for%20%24105%20a%20month%2C%20after%20you%20pay%20%24160%20for%20two%20lab%20exams.%20Some%20clinics%20offer%20discounts%20if%20you%20sign%20up%20for%20six%20months%20or%20a%20year%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGameday%20Men's%20Health%2C%20quickly%20becoming%20a%20main%20player%20in%20the%20space%2C%20does%20not%20offer%20telehealth%2C%20and%20regular%20lab%20work%20is%20required%20and%20performed%20on-site.%20In%20lieu%20of%20the%20convenience%20of%20telehealth%2C%20it%20offers%20%26quot%3Ba%20man-cave%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20Evan%20Miller%2C%20Gameday's%20founder%20and%20CEO%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gameday%20Men's%20Health%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671aae2e9b3250dbbce9f534%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223363%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGameday%20Men's%20Health%20offers%20%26quot%3Ba%20man%20cave%20environment%26quot%3B%20for%20their%20patients%2C%20according%20to%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Evan%20Miller.%3Cp%3EGameday%20Men's%20Health%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGuys%20are%20hanging%20out%20in%20the%20lobby%2C%20watching%20ESPN%2C%20eating%20fruit%20snacks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20guy%20who%20walks%20in%20the%20door%2C%20we%20just%20make%20him%20feel%20like%20a%20brother%2C%20help%20him%20feel%20the%20best%20he%20can%20under%20medical%20guidelines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272b1a0c9-f5fe-4265-9767-a1b30c4f6951%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20it%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETestosterone%20deficiency%20requiring%20medical%20intervention%20is%20not%20common%2C%20nor%20is%20it%20an%20inevitability%20awaiting%20all%20men%20as%20they%20hit%20middle%20or%20even%20old%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20has%20found%20about%2020%25%20of%20young%20men%20are%20considered%20low%20in%20testosterone%20or%20hypogonadal%2C%20a%20condition%20in%20which%20the%20body's%20sex%20glands%20produce%20little%20to%20no%20hormones.%20However%2C%20there's%20disagreement%20about%20what's%20considered%20a%20normal%20range%2C%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eattempts%20at%20establishing%20clinical%20definitions%20for%20low%20testosterone%20and%20andropause%20(%26quot%3Bmale%20menopause%26quot%3B)%20have%20stalled.%20Testosterone%20levels%20also%20fluctuate%20throughout%20a%20man's%20life%2C%20even%20within%20a%20given%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20is%20common%20in%20medicine%2C%20the%20symptoms%20that%20might%20warrant%20a%20prescription%20are%20vague%20and%20ubiquitous.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3255409%2F%23ref12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETelltale%20signs%20of%20low%20testosterone%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20reduced%20libido%2C%20fatigue%2C%20osteoporosis%20and%20fractures%2C%20and%20erectile%20dysfunction%20%E2%80%94%20things%20that%20are%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Erelatively%20prevalent%20among%20men%20to%20varying%20degrees%20and%20for%20different%20reasons.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7520594%2F%23b4-enm-2020-760%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EObesity%20and%20type%202%20diabetes%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20associated%20with%20low%20testosterone%2C%20though%20it's%20unclear%20whether%20a%20testosterone%20dip%20influences%20these%20conditions%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7520594%2F%23b5-enm-2020-760%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20other%20way%20around%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20Derek%2C%20a%2038-year-old%20glazier%20from%20Southern%20California%2C%20was%20reading%20Men's%20Health%20magazine%20when%20he%20came%20across%20an%20article%20about%20testosterone-replacement%20therapy.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20symptoms%20that%20were%20described%20in%20there%20were%20fitting%20my%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20Derek%2C%20who%20asked%20to%20withhold%20his%20last%20name%20for%20privacy%2C%20told%20me.%20These%20were%20symptoms%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20massive%2C%20massive%20amount%20of%20fatigue%2C%26quot%3B%20erectile%20dysfunction%2C%20poor%20sleep%20quality%2C%20excess%20body%20fat%2C%20and%20inability%20to%20put%20on%20muscle%20despite%20diet%20and%20exercise%20changes%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDerek%20searched%20for%20clinics%20online%20and%20arrived%20at%20Gameday%20Men's%20Health.%20A%20year%20and%20a%20half%20of%20weekly%20injections%20later%2C%20he%20can't%20contain%20his%20excitement.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20testosterone.%20I%20would%20never%20stop%20taking%20testosterone%2C%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%20on%20the%20phone.%20These%20days%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20has%20enough%20energy%20to%20work%20two%20jobs%20seven%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDana%2C%2045%2C%20a%20roofer%20and%20grip%20on%20movie%20sets%20in%20California%2C%20said%20he%20used%20to%20roll%20his%20eyes%20at%20%26quot%3Bcheesy%26quot%3B%20commercials%20for%20%26quot%3BT-boosting%26quot%3B%20products%20that%20promised%20%26quot%3Byou'll%20have%20so%20much%20energy%20and%20you'll%20perform%20better%20in%20the%20bedroom.%26quot%3B%20But%20things%20changed%20in%20his%2040s.%20He%20said%20that%20after%20%26quot%3Bhitting%20a%20plateau%20in%20the%20gym%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20decided%20to%20try%20out%20TRT%2C%20telling%20himself%20he%20could%20always%20stop%20if%20he%20didn't%20like%20it.%20Within%20four%20weeks%2C%20he%20noticed%20increased%20energy%20levels%2C%20and%20his%20wife%20noticed%20a%20spike%20in%20his%20libido.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20he's%20sold%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20maintaining%20your%20T%20levels.%20%26quot%3BThe%20energy%2C%20the%20libido%2C%20and%20the%20physical%20gains%20in%20the%20gym%20are%2C%20like%2C%20the%20three%20top%20sellers%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Dana%2C%20who%20also%20asked%20to%20withhold%20his%20last%20name%20for%20privacy%2C%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20why%20it's%20not%20more%20talked%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20TRT%20work%20for%20every%20man%20like%20it%20has%20for%20Kade%2C%20Derek%2C%20and%20Dana%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20cite%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40kmartfit%2Fvideo%2F7420908769862847786%5C%22%20data-video-id%3D%5C%227420908769862847786%5C%22%3E%20%3Csection%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40kmartfit%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%40kmartfit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40kmartfit%3C%2Fa%3E%20Testosterone%20Replacement%20Therapy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Ftrt%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22trt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23Trt%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Ftrtgains%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22trtgains%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23trtgains%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Ftrt101%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22trt101%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23trt101%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Ftrtfamily%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22trtfamily%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23trtfamily%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Ftrttransformation%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22trttransformation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23trttransformation%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Ftrtshots%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22trtshots%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23trtshots%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Ftrtshot%3Frefer%3Dem