2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2017%2F03%2F28%2Fwell%2Ftestosterone-therapy-is-popular-but-studies-are-mixed.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20be%20mixed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F29562341%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrials%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20too%20small%20to%20glean%20anything%20from%20or%20feature%20only%20older%20men%2C%20leaving%20unanswered%20questions%20about%20how%20TRT%20affects%20men%20below%2035.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20solid%20evidence%20that%20hypogonadal%20men%20treated%20with%20TRT%20may%20experience%20increased%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1111%2Fcob.12022%23cob12022-bib-0004%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emuscle%20mass%20and%20reduced%20fat%20mass%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20for%20a%20few%20weeks.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F37589949%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20the%20few%20long-term%20studies%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20middle-aged%20and%20older%20men%20who%20took%20TRT%20to%20boost%20testosterone%20and%20libido%20had%20more%20energy%2C%20better%20sex%2C%20and%20more%20sexual%20desire%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20the%20downsides%20are%20real%3A%20hair%20loss%2C%20acne%2C%20and%20a%20possible%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mayoclinic.org%2Fhealthy-lifestyle%2Fsexual-health%2Fin-depth%2Ftestosterone-therapy%2Fart-20045728%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworsening%20of%20sleep%20apnea%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Infertility%2C%20too%3A%20Urologists%20across%20the%20country%20told%20me%20that%20they%20had%20fielded%20a%20surprising%20number%20of%20puzzled%20young%20patients%20who%20weren't%20aware%20that%20boosting%20testosterone%20also%20decreases%20sperm%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20seeing%20more%20and%20more%20young%20men%20come%20to%20the%20office%20on%20TRT%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Justin%20Dubin%2C%20a%20urologist%20in%20Miami%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20coming%20for%20fertility%20care.%20And%20basically%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'Well%2C%20are%20you%20on%20TRT%3F'%20And%20they're%20like%2C%20'Yeah.'%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'Well%2C%20that%20kills%20your%20sperm.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDubin%20was%20curious%20about%20this%2C%20so%20he%20did%20a%20secret-shopper%20study%20on%20direct-to-consumer%20companies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamainternalmedicine%2Ffullarticle%2F2799297%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20in%20JAMA%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022.%20Posing%20as%20a%2034-year-old%20patient%20with%20above-average%20testosterone%20levels%2C%20he%20contacted%20these%20clinics%20and%20said%20he%20was%20interested%20in%20preserving%20his%20fertility.%20Six%20of%20the%20seven%20companies%20offered%20him%20testosterone%20despite%20the%20contraindication.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20pretty%20awakening%20study%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2276a3d450-e3bb-4fa0-acc1-7f34f12d3132%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20new%20kind%20of%20gender-affirming%20care%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMen's%20health%20clinics%20are%2C%20in%20general%2C%20operating%20in%20a%20gray%20area%20of%20medicine.%20This%20is%20not%20your%20primary-care%20doctor%20taking%20a%20holistic%20perspective%20of%20your%20health%20needs.%20This%20is%20a%20business%20selling%20a%20supplement%20%E2%80%94%20a%20boost%20to%20add%20to%20your%20routine%20to%20feel%20more%20like%20the%20cultural%20ideal%20of%20a%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrucially%2C%20these%20clinics%20do%20not%20cater%20to%20trans%20men.%20Clinic%20directors%20proudly%20shared%20with%20me%20the%20diversity%20of%20their%20patients%20%E2%80%94%20from%20bricklayers%20to%20CEOs.%20When%20I%20asked%20about%20transgender%20care%2C%20they%20demurred.%20That's%20something%20else%2C%20they%20said.%20Too%20complicated%2C%20too%20specific.%20Snedegar%20told%20me%20his%20clinic%20took%20only%20%26quot%3Bbiological%20men.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20social%20scientists%20have%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20implications%20this%20trend%20has%20for%20broader%20cultural%20understandings%20of%20masculinity.%20Gwen%20Berumen%2C%20a%20sociologist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Texas%20at%20Austin%2C%20has%20analyzed%20the%20emergence%20of%20testosterone%20discourse%20on%20TikTok%20and%20found%20clinics%20and%20influencers%20to%20be%20hyperfocused%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20%26quot%3Boptimizing%26quot%3B%20your%20body%20to%20achieve%20an%20elusive%20masculine%20state.%20%26quot%3BAnything%20that's%20about%20self-optimization%20is%20trying%20to%20reach%20this%20ideal%20that%20you're%20never%20actually%20going%20to%20get%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Berumen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20American%20Psychological%20Association%20issued%20its%20first-ever%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apa.org%2Fmonitor%2F2019%2F01%2Fce-corner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarning%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20perils%20of%20masculinity.%20The%20organization%20said%20the%20strict%20standards%20of%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20a%20man%20today%20were%20making%20boys%20and%20men%20feel%20isolated%2C%20weak%2C%20and%20unable%20to%20express%20themselves.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EResearchers%20such%20as%20Berumen%20worry%20the%20branding%20of%20men's%20health%20clinics%20prop%20up%20impossible%20standards%20of%20manhood.%20The%20implication%20is%20that%20the%20only%20thing%20between%20you%20and%20unbridled%20manly%20perfection%20is%20a%20will%20and%20a%20syringe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMedicalized%20masculinity%20has%20higher%20stakes%2C%20Berumen%20said.%20Gender-affirming%20care%20is%20becoming%20more%20accessible%2C%20but%20only%20for%20one%20kind%20of%20man%3A%20Testosterone%20clinics%20for%20cisgender%20men%20are%20proliferating%20amid%20a%20wave%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fgraphics%2FUSA-HEALTHCARE%2FTRANS-BILLS%2Fzgvorreyapd%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanti-trans%20legislation%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20limits%20access%20for%20transgender%20Americans.%20While%20testosterone%20therapy%20for%20cisgender%20men%20may%20or%20may%20not%20be%20beneficial%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20there's%20strong%20evidence%20that%20testosterone%20treatment%20is%20associated%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flandia%2Farticle%2FPIIS2213-8587(16)00036-X%2Fabstract%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimproved%20mental%20and%20physical%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jahonline.org%2Farticle%2FS1054-139X(21)00568-1%2Ffulltext%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20levels%20of%20suicidality%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20trans%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20upsides%20to%20the%20expansion%20of%20DTC%20men's%20health.%20Dubin%2C%20the%20Miami%20urologist%2C%20has%20his%20doubts%20about%20this%20industry%20but%20said%20inspiring%20men%20to%20care%20about%20their%20health%20is%20a%20good%20thing.%20Men%20have%20long%20underused%20the%20healthcare%20system%20and%20historically%20engage%20in%20less%20%26quot%3Bhealthy%26quot%3B%20behaviors%20than%20women%2C%20like%20eating%20well%20and%20seeing%20a%20doctor%20regularly.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20more%20approachable%20for%20many%20men%20to%20talk%20about%20their%20health%20problems%20this%20way%2C%20especially%20men's%20health%20problems%2C%20which%20have%20a%20stigma%20around%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Dubin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20clinics%20are%20also%20helping%20men%20forge%20networks%20of%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20day%20I%20wake%20up%2C%20I%20read%20my%20DMs%2C%20I%20read%20my%20comments%2C%20and%20I%20go%20film%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Kade%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20on%20fire%20to%20help%20other%20men%20create%20a%20great%20community%20of%20people%20that%20are%20bettering%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20ori