hussman-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJohn%20Hussman%3C%2Fa%3E%20urges%20investors%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20return%20outcomes%20ultimately%20have%20different%20probabilities%20based%20on%20when%20you%20buy%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Faverage-stock-market-return%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520S%2526P%2520500%2520has%2520returned%2Cbonds%2520or%2520fixed%252Dincome%2520assets.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20averaged%2010.5%25%20annual%20returns%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%201957%2C%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20those%20are%20the%20average%20returns%20you'll%20get%20no%20matter%20when%20you%20enter%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20like%20stepping%20into%20a%20house%20with%20two%20rooms%2C%20one%20with%20the%20temperature%20at%200%20degrees%20and%20one%20at%20140%20degrees%2C%20and%20expecting%20a%20temperature%20of%2070%20either%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hussman%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Hussman%20Investment%20Trust%20who%20called%20the%202000%20and%202008%20crashes%2C%20in%20an%20October%2017%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECase%20in%20point%2C%20if%20you%20bought%20in%20on%20February%2014%2C%202020%2C%20you'd%20be%20up%2071%25.%20But%20if%20you%20bought%20in%20just%20over%20a%20month%20later%2C%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20pandemic-driven%20crash%20on%20March%2020%2C%20you'd%20be%20up%20152%25%20right%20now.%20They're%20both%20great%20outcomes%2C%20no%20doubt.%20But%20they're%20very%20different.%20And%20in%20business%20cycles%20where%20monetary%20and%20fiscal%20stimulus%20aren't%20as%20robust%2C%20the%20market%20can%20take%20a%20much%20longer%20time%20to%20recover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20a%20few%20different%20variables%20show%20that%20investors%20should%20expect%20poor%20outcomes%20over%20the%20next%2012%20years%20if%20they%20were%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20today%2C%20Hussman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20there%20are%20valuation%20levels.%20Hussman's%20go-to%20measure%20is%20the%20market%20cap%20of%20non-financial%20stocks%20divided%20by%20those%20stocks'%20total%20gross%20value%20added.%20The%20metric%20is%20at%20all-time%20highs%2C%20surpassing%20the%20largest%20bubble%20peaks%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22909%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22stock%20valuations%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671c0db69b3250dbbcea6129%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22520%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHussman%20Funds%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHussman%20likes%20it%20so%20much%20because%20it's%20been%20a%20fairly%20good%20predictor%20of%2012-year%20market%20returns%20relative%20to%2010-year%20Treasury%20returns.%20Here's%20the%20relationship%20between%20expectations%20and%20actual%20market%20returns.%20Current%20expectations%20have%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20underperforming%20Treasurys%20by%209.9%25%20annually%20over%20the%20next%2012%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22911%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22expected%20vs%20actual%20market%20returns%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671c0de09b3250dbbcea6134%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22526%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHussman%20Funds%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20investor%20sentiment%2C%20which%20Hussman%20measures%20through%20the%20uniformity%20of%20movement%20in%20thousands%20of%20securities.%20In%20the%20chart%20below%2C%20when%20the%20measure%20goes%20flat%20like%20in%202000%20and%202008%2C%20it's%20historically%20been%20bad%20for%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22915%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hussman%20market%20internals%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671c0e05a0a0cc14f22436bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22522%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHussman%20Funds%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20there's%20the%20accumulation%20of%20warning%20signs%20of%20market%20over-extension%20that%20rivals%20prior%20major%20downturn%20periods.%20The%20individual%20warning%20signs%20that%20Hussman%20monitors%20are%20various%20technical%20indicators%2C%20like%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20being%20within%202%25%20of%20its%205-year%20high%20while%20less%20than%2072%25%20of%20stocks%20are%20below%20their%20200-day%20moving%20averages%20and%202.5%25%20of%20stocks%20hit%20new%20both%2052-week%20highs%20and%20lows%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20among%20other%20conflicting%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22906%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hussman%20market%20over-extension%20signals%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671c0e49a0a0cc14f22436cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22523%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHussman%20Funds%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d60fe598-14e2-4ac5-a790-8f742704fa81%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHussman's%20track%20record%20%E2%80%94%20and%20his%20views%20in%20context%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHussman's%20outlook%20is%20often%20seen%20as%20extreme%2C%20and%20perhaps%20fairly%20so.%20But%20valuations%20are%20causing%20skepticism%20about%20future%20market%20returns%20among%20others%20on%20Wall%20Street%2C%20even%20if%20not%20to%20the%20same%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-sp500-future-returns-decade-forecast-goldman-sachs-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20forecast%20that%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20would%20average%203%25%20annual%20returns%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%20That's%20less%20than%20the%204.2%25%20annual%20yield%20that%20risk-free%2010-year%20Treasurys%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20worth%20remembering%20that%20Hussman's%20outlook%20is%20only%20for%20a%2012-year%20period%20if%20you%20were%20to%20buy%20in%20now%20%E2%80%94%20not%20if%20you%20plan%20to%20hold%20for%20multiple%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20uninitiated%2C%20Hussman%20has%20repeatedly%20made%20headlines%20by%20predicting%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-news-john-hussman-says-stocks-at-record-valuations-will-lose-two-thirds-2018-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estock-market%20decline%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20exceeding%2060%25%20and%20forecasting%20a%20full%20decade%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-news-market-bear-sees-decade-of-stock-losses-wall-street-mad-2017-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enegative%20equity%20returns%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20as%20the%20stock%20market%20ground%20mostly%20higher%2C%20he%20persisted%20with%20his%20doomsday%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20you%20dismiss%20Hussman%20as%20a%20wonky%20perma-bear%2C%20consider%20again%20his%20track%20record.%20Here%20are%20the%20arguments%20he's%20laid%20out%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20predicted%20in%20March%202000%20that%20tech%20stocks%20would%20plunge%2083%25%2C%20and%20then%20the%20tech-heavy%20Nasdaq%20100%20index%20lost%20an%20%26quot%3Bimprobably%20precise%26quot%3B%2083%25%20during%20a%20period%20from%202000%20to%202002.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20predicted%20in%202000%20that%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20would%20probably%20see%20negative%20total%20returns%20over%20the%20following%20decade%2C%20which%20it%20did.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20predicted%20in%20April%202007%20that%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20could%20lose%2040%25%2C%20then%20it%20lost%2055%25%20in%20the%20subsequent%20collapse%20from%202007%20to%202009.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHussman's%20recent%20returns%2C%20however%2C%20have%20been%20less%20than%20stellar.%20His%20Strategic%20Growth%20Fund%20is%20down%20about%2055%25%20since%20December%202010%20and%20has%20fallen%2016%25%20in%20the%20past%2012%20months.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20by%20comparison%2C%20is%20up%20about%2039%25%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20of%20bearish%20evidence%20being%20unearthed%20by%20Hussman%20continues%20to%20mount%2C%20and%20his%20calls%20over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%20for%20a%20substantial%20sell-off%20began%20to%20prove%20accurate%20in%202022.%20Yes%2C%20there%20may%20still%20be%20returns%20to%20be%20realized%20in%20this%20new%20bull%20market%2C%20but%20at%20what%20point%20does%20the%20mounting%20risk%20of%20a%20larger%20crash%20become%20too%20unbearable%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20question%20investors%20will%20have%20to%20answer%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20and%20one%20that%20Hussman%20will%20keep%20exploring%20in%20the%20interim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-terrible-time-to-invest-sp500-bubble-hussman-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729933202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661030981caec1275a6d4eea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-terrible-time-to-invest-sp500-bubble-hussman-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Before%20investing%20in%20stocks%2C%20John%20Hussman%20urges%20investors%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20return%20outcomes%20depend%20on%20when%20you%20buy%20in.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-terrible-time-to-invest-sp500-bubble-hussman-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shweta%20Tiwari's%20guide%20to%20casual%20and%20chic%20style%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729933000000%2C%22visual%22