0According%20to%20one%20group%20of%20analysts%2C%20the%20strike%20has%20cost%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-strike-costing-50m-per-day-as-negotiations-restart-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2450%20million%20a%20day%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrtberg%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20released%20to%20employees%20along%20with%20the%20company's%20third-quarter%20results%2C%20said%20Boeing's%20customers%20want%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20need%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20company%20to%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20right%20focus%20and%20culture%2C%20we%20can%20be%20an%20iconic%20company%20and%20aerospace%20leader%20once%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20offered%20a%20reminder%20that%20Ortberg%20has%20to%20balance%20pressures%20from%20workers%2C%20investors%2C%20and%20Boeing's%20customers.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20the%20company's%20commercial%20business%2C%20which%20builds%20aircraft%20for%20airlines%2C%20that%20ultimately%20means%20the%20flying%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBill%20George%2C%20the%20former%20CEO%20of%20medical%20device%20maker%20Medtronic%20and%20an%20executive%20fellow%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20Ortberg%20has%20to%20tackle%20short-term%20challenges%20like%20the%20worker%20strike%20and%20shoring%20up%20cash%20flow%20while%20also%20making%20%26quot%3Bbold%20decisions%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20can't%20just%20do%20one%20or%20the%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20George%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22344697db-407e-4770-8539-290cb807cfc8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERestoring%20a%20culture%20of%20safety%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGeorge%20said%20that%20while%20the%20company's%20commercial%2C%20defense%2C%20and%20space%20businesses%20each%20face%20challenges%20individually%2C%20the%20broader%20issue%20that%20needs%20prioritizing%20is%20restoring%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business