20Stuxnet%20virus%20took%20out%20the%20enrichment%20centrifuges%20at%20Natanz.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20accused%20Israel%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20while%20information%20security%20experts%20also%20pointed%20the%20finger%20at%20Washington.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIran's%20allies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran's%20allies%20too%20have%20found%20that%20Tehran%20is%20not%20always%20safe%20shelter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20political%20chief%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20was%20killed%20on%20July%2031%20in%20Iran's%20capital%20in%20an%20attack%20blamed%20on%20Israel.%20He%20was%20in%20Tehran%20to%20attend%20the%20inauguration%20ceremony%20of%20Iran's%20new%20president%20Masoud%20Pezeshkian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIranian%20petrol%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202021%2C%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%20citing%20US%20and%20Middle%20East%20officials%2C%20reported%20that%20Israel%20had%20in%202019%20targeted%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20vessels%20travelling%20to%20Syria%20and%20in%20most%20cases%2C%20transporting%20Iranian%20petrol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20Israel%20had%20deployed%20underwater%20mines%20in%20the%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%202021%2C%20Israel%20and%20Iran%20accused%20each%20other%20of%20naval%20sabotages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729924440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fnp9d7e3o_israel-offensive-against-iran_625x300_26_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fassassinations-cyberattacks-how-israel-pulled-up-offensive-against-iran-6877111%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20hitjobs%20to%20sabotages%20and%20cyberattacks%2C%20Israel%20has%20either%20been%20blamed%20for%20or%20has%20itself%20claimed%20a%20variety%20