air%20quality%20improved%20slightly%20on%20Saturday%20morning%20nearly%20four%20days%20after%20the%20national%20capital%20reeled%20under%20toxic%20air%20pollution%2C%20however%2C%20it%20still%20remains%20in%20the%20'poor'%20category.%20The%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20in%20Delhi%20dropped%20to%20230%20this%20morning%20-%20from%20Friday's%20reading%20of%20270.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Air%20Quality%20Early%20Warning%20System%20(AQEWS)%2C%20the%20air%20quality%20in%20Delhi%20has%20improved%20due%20to%20a%20sudden%20change%20in%20wind%20direction%20and%20speed.%20Despite%20the%20improvement%2C%20weather%20experts%20have%20cautioned%20that%20the%20relief%20may%20be%20short-lived%2C%20as%20pollution%20levels%20are%20expected%20to%20rise%20again%20in%20the%20next%20three%20days%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20quality%20index%20is%20likely%20to%20touch%20400%20by%20October%2031%2C%20the%20weather%20system%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFearing%20further%20air%20quality%20deterioration%20after%20Diwali%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20has%20imposed%20stage%20two%20of%20the%20GRAP%20or%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-aqi-anti-pollution-plan-on-delhi-air-quality-remains-very-poor-6852128%5C%22%3E%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Under%20this%20stage%2C%20there%20are%20restrictions%20on%20the%20use%20of%20coal%2C%20firewood%2C%20and%20diesel%20generator%20sets%20across%20Delhi-NCR.%20The%20administration%20will%20carry%20out%20mechanical%20sweeping%20and%20water%20sprinkling%20on%20roads%20daily%2C%20while%20people%20have%20been%20advised%20to%20use%20public%20transport%20and%20minimize%20the%20use%20of%20personal%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Delhi%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20conducted%20a%20demonstration%20showcasing%20drone-based%20services%20to%20identify%20sources%20of%20pollution%20in%20hotspot%20areas.%20He%20also%2