tion%20to%20Harris's%20rally%2C%20which%20focused%20on%20abortion%20restrictions%20in%20Republican-led%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyonce%20said%20she%20was%20not%20there%20as%20a%20celebrity%20but%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20mother%20who%20cares%20deeply%20about%20the%20world...%20a%20world%20where%20we%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20control%20our%20bodies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETexas%20is%20not%20one%20of%20the%20handful%20of%20battlegrounds%20that%20are%20expected%20to%20decide%20the%20presidential%20election%2C%20or%20where%20the%20Democrat%20and%20her%20rival%20would%20normally%20be%20campaigning%20in%20the%20home%20stretch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Harris%20is%20banking%20on%20her%20star-studded%20show%20--%20which%20also%20featured%2091-year-old%20country%20legend%20Willie%20Nelson%2C%20who%20sang%20%26quot%3BMamma%2C%20don't%20let%20them%20babies%20grow%20up%20to%20be%20cowboys%26quot%3B%20--%20to%20energize%20her%20campaign%20ahead%20of%20the%20final%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVoting%20has%20already%20started%2C%20and%20we%20know%20this%20will%20be%20a%20tight%20race%20until%20the%20very%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%2011%20days%20out%20from%20an%20election%20that%20will%20decide%20the%20future%20of%20America%2C%20including%20the%20freedom%20of%20every%20woman%20to%20make%20decisions%20about%20her%20own%20body.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Fascist'%20row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Harris%20was%20in%20Houston%2C%20Trump%20was%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Austin%2C%20taping%20an%20interview%20with%20%26quot%3BThe%20Joe%20Rogan%20Experience%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20United%20States'%20most%20popular%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20follow-on%20rally%2C%20in%20battleground%20Michigan%2C%20was%20delayed%20after%20his%20taping%20with%20Rogan%20ran%20on%20for%20three%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20and%20Trump%20also%20locked%20horns%20earlier%20Friday%20over%20accusations%20that%20the%20Republican%20ex-president%20has%20been%20running%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfascist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20camps%20traded%20barbs%20over%20claims%20by%20Trump's%20longest-serving%20White%20House%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20echoed%20by%20Harris%2C%20that%20Trump%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bfascist%26quot%3B%20who%20cannot%20be%20trusted%20with%20power%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepublican%20leaders%20in%20Congress%20attacked%20her%20over%20that%20characterization%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20revealing%20they%20had%20been%20briefed%20on%20%26quot%3Bongoing%20and%20persistent%26quot%3B%20threats%20to%20Trump%2C%20and%20accused%20Harris%20of%20encouraging%20%26quot%3Banother%20would-be%20assassin%26quot%3B%20after%20he%20survived%20an%20attempt%20on%20his%20life%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Garbage%20can'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHalf%20the%20country%20agrees%20with%20Harris%20that%20Trump%20is%20a%20fascist%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20ABC%20News%2FIpsos%20poll%20of%20registered%20voters%2C%20and%20she%20hit%20back%20at%20an%20impromptu%20news%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20truth%20is%20that%20some%20of%20the%20people%20closest%20to%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20when%20he%20was%20president...%20have%20been%20very%20clear%20about%20the%20danger%20and%20the%20threat%20that%20(he)%20poses%20to%20America%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20is%20unfit%20to%20serve%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20American%20people%20deserve%20to%20hear%20that%2C%20and%20know%20about%20that%2C%20so%20they%20can%20make%20a%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20described%20the%20United%20States%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bgarbage%20can%20for%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20second%20time%20this%20week%20while%20giving%20remarks%20in%20Austin%20--%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20string%20of%20inflammatory%20comments%20on%20immigration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20race%20is%20a%20dead%20heat