0and%20then%20pressed%20on%20a%20hot%20%3Cem%3Etava%20%3C%2Fem%3E(pan)%20laden%20with%20%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20the%20late%2070s%2C%20each%20%3Cem%3Etikki%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20around%20Rs%2020%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20money!%20But%20the%20crispiness%20of%20those%20potatoes%20is%20very%20nostalgic%20for%20me.%20I%20still%20snack%20on%20them%20when%20I%20go%20to%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Khanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%E2%80%99d%20be%20interested%20to%20know%20that%20this%20spot%20is%20one%20of%20the%20seven%20distinguished%20ones%20dotting%20the%20%E2%80%98food%20map%E2%80%99%20devised%20by%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20mother%20to%20celebrate%20his%20homecoming.%20The%20locales%20are%20set%20in%20stone%20and%20nothing%20is%20up%20for%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20her%20son%E2%80%99s%20global%20fame%20means%20the%20duo%20can%20no%20longer%20feast%20on%20%3Cem%3Etikkis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Echaat%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246397%2Fstreet-food-vendors-pav-bhaji-american-civil-war-cotton-mill-portugese-mumbai-video-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estreet%20food)%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20peace%20without%20500-odd%20people%20thronging%20to%20get%20a%20glimpse%20of%20their%20favourite%20chef%20or%20(if%20they%E2%80%99re%20lucky)%20a%20selfie.%20And%20Khanna%20is%20ever-obliging%2C%20animatedly%20chatting%20up%20each%20vendor%20he%20visits.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20all%2C%20they%20were%20my%20foundation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20perfectly%20segues%20his%20next%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20often%20take%20things%20for%20granted%20when%20we%20have%20them.%E2%80%9