02%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-3-1729603781.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20data-recalc-dims%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371670%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20interiors%20of%20Bungalow%20have%20been%20done%20keeping%20Indian%20aesthetic%20in%20mind%3B%20the%20restaurant%20is%20an%20invitation%20to%20experience%20Indian%20culture%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20today%2C%20the%20menu%20at%20Bungalow%20in%20East%20Village%2C%20New%20York%2C%20reflects%20these%20sensibilities.%20Time%20and%20again%2C%20the%20culinary%20virtuoso%20has%20reiterated%20how%20his%20latest%20%E2%80%94%20and%20last%20%E2%80%94%20gastronomic%20endeavour%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20street%20vendors%20of%20India%20and%20the%20crafts%20they%20have%20perfected%20over%20generations.%20%E2%80%9CI%20hail%20from%20a%20small%20town%2C%20a%20small%20community%20where%20street%20food%20was%20the%20only%20way.%20In%20my%20growing%20up%20years%2C%20there%20was%20just%20one%20restaurant%20in%20Amritsar.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20food%20of%20street%20vendors%20that%20made%20us%20go%20%E2%80%98wow%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorrowing%20from%20the%20English%20word%20for%20%3Cem%3Ebangla%20%3C%2Fem%3E(single-story%20home)%2C%20coined%20during%20India%E2%80%99s%20colonial%20past%2C%20Bungalow%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307799%2Flondon-oldest-indian-restaurant-veeraswamy-history-nehru-gandhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvitation%20to%20experience%20history%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20exceptional%20cuisine.%20With%20a%20menu%20featuring%20a%20repository%20of%20time-honoured%20recipes%20documented%20from%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%2028%20states%20in%20all%20its%2